name: Dual CD Player with Two 6.5" Speakers and Hands-free Kit

reviews.name: Dual CD Player with Two 6.5" Speakers and Hands-free Kit
reviews.reviewText: We gave this car stereo system to my daughter for Christmas, and it exceeded all our expectations! Love having the ability to play music from iPhone or iPod, and having the USB port available to charge the devices is even better. CD and radio sound great, too. Speakers did not fit in her 1991 Honda Accord, but since the old ones still work, no problem for us. Love it!
reviews.title: Amazing features for a low price!

reviews.name: Dual CD Player with Two 6.5" Speakers and Hands-free Kit
reviews.reviewText: The radio is not as fancy as most but it does look nice but it has features that it makes up for. The radio has a phone charger built in, so just plug you phone in on the go and never worry about haveing a seprate charger. YOu can plug in your Mp3 player. This set comes with 2 speakers so if need be you have extra for your car if one goes out. It also comes with hands free device for you cell phone. For the price you can't beat it! Just order it to be sent to the store cause the website with say its available in store and its not. They still have to end up shipping it.
reviews.title: A lot of a Good Price

reviews.name: Dual CD Player with Two 6.5" Speakers and Hands-free Kit
reviews.reviewText: easy to install sounds good phone holder works phone speaker works I would recommend this to anyone in need of a inexpensive radio with speakers and hands free talking while driving.
reviews.title: great radio for thr price
